11#include "call/adaptation/video_stream_input_state_provider.h"
12
13#include "call/adaptation/video_stream_adapter.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17VideoStreamInputStateProvider::VideoStreamInputStateProvider(
18 VideoStreamEncoderObserver* frame_rate_provider)
19 : frame_rate_provider_(frame_rate_provider) {}
20
21VideoStreamInputStateProvider::~VideoStreamInputStateProvider() {}
22
23void VideoStreamInputStateProvider::OnHasInputChanged(bool has_input) {
24 MutexLock lock(&mutex_);
25 input_state_.set_has_input(has_input);
26}
27
28void VideoStreamInputStateProvider::OnFrameSizeObserved(int frame_size_pixels) {
29 RTC_DCHECK_GT(frame_size_pixels, 0);
30 MutexLock lock(&mutex_);
31 input_state_.set_frame_size_pixels(frame_size_pixels);
32}
33
34void VideoStreamInputStateProvider::OnEncoderSettingsChanged(
35 EncoderSettings encoder_settings) {
36 MutexLock lock(&mutex_);
37 input_state_.set_video_codec_type(
38 encoder_settings.encoder_config().codec_type);
39 input_state_.set_min_pixels_per_frame(
40 encoder_settings.encoder_info().scaling_settings.min_pixels_per_frame);
41 input_state_.set_single_active_stream_pixels(
42 VideoStreamAdapter::GetSingleActiveLayerPixels(
43 encoder_settings.video_codec()));
44}
45
46VideoStreamInputState VideoStreamInputStateProvider::InputState() {
47 // GetInputFrameRate() is thread-safe.
48 int input_fps = frame_rate_provider_->GetInputFrameRate();
49 MutexLock lock(&mutex_);
50 input_state_.set_frames_per_second(input_fps);
51 return input_state_;
52}
53
54} // namespace webrtc
